parameters.name: OrderActionDetail
parameters.description: The parameters that are used to filter SQL statements involved in the ticket.

parameters.name: OrderId
parameters.description: The ID of the ticket for the SQL review. You can call the [CreateSQLReviewOrder](~~257777~~) operation to query the ID of the ticket.

parameters.name: Tid
parameters.description: The ID of the tenant. You can call the [GetUserActiveTenant](~~198073~~) or [ListUserTenants](~~465818~~) operation to query the ID of the tenant.
